snippet.title: Delivering Hope V3.0.0 Promo Video
snippet.description:
Delivering Hope is a hololive fangame where you throw IRyS (hololive English VSinger) and try to fly as far as you can.

Choose your launch angle and power, hit powerups to propel you further ahead, buy upgrades as IRyS levels up during the run, and avoid hitting Bae at all costs!

This is a free fan-made game created following COVER Corp's derivative works guidelines. This is not an official hololive game.

The developer is not endorsed nor affiliated with hololive, COVER Corp, or any of its talents. All holopro talents are ©2016 COVER Corp.
